  <li>
    <p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px;"><font size="2"><a href="legislation/legislation_ireland.html"><b>Ireland&nbsp;&gt;&gt;</b></a></font></li>
  <li>
    <p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px;"><b><font size="2"><a href="legislation/legislation_italy.html">Italy</a></font><a href="legislation/legislation_italy.html">
    &gt;&gt;</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="law.html">Find more&gt;&gt;</a></b></li>
</ul>
<p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px;">Please, help us in updating the <b><a href="#" onclick="window.open('spam_submission.asp', 'Survey', 'width=660, height=600, scrollbars=yes');"><font color="#FF9900">ITU
anti-spam survey</font></a></b>
                        <p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px;">If you have comments, or would
like to provide any additional information, please contact the ITU Strategy and
Policy Unit (SPU) at <a href="mailto:cybersecurity@itu.int">cybersecurity (at) itu.int</a>.
                        </td>
